.TH MPI_File_get_amode 3 "12/7/2007" " " "MPI"
.SH NAME
MPI_File_get_amode \-  Returns the file access mode 
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
int MPI_File_get_amode(MPI_File mpi_fh, int *amode)
.fi
.SH INPUT PARAMETERS
.PD 0
.TP
.B fh 
- file handle (handle)
.PD 1

.SH OUTPUT PARAMETERS
.PD 0
.TP
.B amode 
- access mode (integer)
.PD 1

